<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-container">
    <div class="footer-disclaimer">
      <span class="footer-disclaimer-icon">⚠️</span>
      <span>当サイトの投資情報は教育目的です。特定銘柄の購入推奨ではありません。</span>
      <a href="/privacy/">詳細</a>
    </div>
    <nav class="footer-nav">
      <a href="/about/">運営者について</a>
      <a href="/privacy/">プライバシーポリシー</a>
      <a href="/contact/">お問い合わせ</a>
    </nav>
    <p class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 会社員の生活日記. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    background: #1e293b;
    color: #94a3b8;
    padding: 2rem 0 1.5rem;
    margin-top: auto;
  }
  .footer-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .footer-disclaimer {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #334155;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .footer-disclaimer a {
    color: #60a5fa;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .footer-disclaimer a:hover { color: #93c5fd; }
  .footer-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  .footer-nav a {
    color: #94a3b8;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }
  .footer-nav a:hover { color: #60a5fa; }
  .footer-copy {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: #64748b;
  }
</style>
